headline: Is Phillips 66 Stock Still Attractive After Its Strong Multi Year Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Phillips 66 is still reasonably priced at its current level or if much of the potential upside has already been realized, this walkthrough will help you assess whether the current market price really makes sense. The stock has climbed 1.8% over the last week and 2.5% over the past month, adding to a 21.8% gain year to date and a 143.7% return over five years.
